Set up environment:

python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate           # Or venv\Scripts\activate on Windows
pip install biopython matplotlib

Save this script as protein_analysis.py.

Run it from the command line, e.g.:

python protein_analysis.py 1FAT
python protein_analysis.py 1FAT --chain A --window 7 --show

Outputs:

Protein info printed to console
Amino acid composition bar chart saved as {PDB_ID}_composition.png
Hydrophobicity plot saved as {PDB_ID}_hydrophobicity.png (or shown interactively with --show)
